                     <interp inst="t18270913-187-off1058" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-187-cd1059" type="crimeDate">12th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-187-off1058 t18270913-187-cd1059"></join>, 1 watch, value 30s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
